<h1>反</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">fǎn</span><span class=alesi>(fan3)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">fàn</span><span class=alesi>(fan4)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 反 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 反</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/reverse" style="color:black;">reverse</a>, <a href="/dictionary/opposite" style="color:black;">opposite</a>, <a href="/dictionary/contrary" style="color:black;">contrary</a>, anti</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 4<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 4 strokes: <a href="/character/不" title="bu4: no, not; un-; negative prefix">不</a>, <a href="/character/中" title="zhong1: central; center, middle; in the midst of; hit (target); attain">中</a>, <a href="/character/为" title="wei4: do, handle, govern, act; be">为</a>, <a href="/character/以" title="yi3: by means of; thereby, therefore; consider as; in order to">以</a>, <a href="/character/方" title="fang1: a square, rectangle; a region; local">方</a>, <a href="/character/天" title="tian1: sky, heaven; god, celestial">天</a>, <a href="/character/分" title="fen1: divide; small unit of time etc.">分</a>, <a href="/character/心" title="xin1: heart; mind, intelligence; soul">心</a>, <a href="/character/开" title="kai1: open; initiate, begin, start">开</a>, <a href="/character/从" title="cong2: from, by, since, whence, through">从</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/又" title="Kangxi radical 29">又</a>&nbsp;29.2</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 4 <br><small>Other HSK 4 characters: <a href="/character/受" title="shou4: receive, accept, get; bear, stand">受</a>, <a href="/character/量" title="liang4: measure, quantity, capacity">量</a>, <a href="/character/建" title="jian4: build, establish, erect, found">建</a>, <a href="/character/何" title="he2: what, why, where, which, how">何</a>, <a href="/character/计" title="ji4: plan, plot; strategem; scheme">计</a>, <a href="/character/管" title="guan3: pipe, tube, duct; woodwind music">管</a>, <a href="/character/尔" title="er3: you; that, those; final particle">尔</a>, <a href="/character/活" title="huo2: live, exist, survive; lively">活</a>, <a href="/character/资" title="zi1: property; wealth; capital">资</a>, <a href="/character/命" title="ming4: life; destiny, fate, luck; an order, instruction">命</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-4" title="List of HSK 4 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 4 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 237</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 0139</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/三反" title="san1 fan3">三反</a>, <a href="/dictionary/倒反" title="dao4 fan3">倒反</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反之" title="fan3 zhi1">反之</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反例" title="fan3 li4">反例</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反倒" title="fan3 dao4">反倒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反侧" title="fan3 ce4">反侧</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反光" title="fan3 guang1">反光</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反共" title="fan3 gong4">反共</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反切" title="fan3 qie4">反切</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反剪" title="fan3 jian3">反剪</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反动" title="fan3 dong4">反动</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反叛" title="fan3 pan4">反叛</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反口" title="fan3 kou3">反口</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反右" title="fan3 you4">反右</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反向" title="fan3 xiang4">反向</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反哺" title="fan3 bu3">反哺</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反问" title="fan3 wen4">反问</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反嘴" title="fan3 zui3">反嘴</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反坐" title="fan3 zuo4">反坐</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反坫" title="fan3 dian4">反坫</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反射" title="fan3 she4">反射</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反对" title="fan3 dui4">反对</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反导" title="fan3 dao3">反导</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反差" title="fan3 cha1">反差</a>, <a href="/dictionary/反帝" title="fan3 di4">反帝</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">反[<span style="color:#009900;">fǎn</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- contrary<br>- in reverse<br>- inside out or ups